'''瑪希拉·罕'''（{{lang-ur|'''ماہرہ خان'''}}，{{lang-en|'''Mahira Khan'''}}，出生名為：Mahira Hafeez Khan，{{bd|1982年|12月21日|catIdx=K}}）是[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]女演員及模特兒，主要出現在巴基斯坦電視連續劇及電影。瑪希拉在2010年演出的電視連續劇《Humsafar》是巴基斯坦史上收視率最高的連續劇，亦使她成為巴國最頂尖的女演員之一。<ref>[http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/humsafar-made-me-popular/ "Humsafar made me popular"] {{Wayback|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/screen/humsafar-made-me-popular/ |date=20160311201631 }}. The Indian Express. 26 September 2014.</ref>

瑪希拉在南部城市[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]出生。她在17歲時前往[[美國|美國]]就讀於[[南加州大学|南加州大学]]但在畢業前便返回巴基斯坦。<ref>[http://www.india.com/top-n/mahira-khan-7-things-to-know-about-humsafars-pretty-khirad-hussain-172850/ "7 things to know about Humsafar's pretty Khirad Hussain"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.india.com/top-n/mahira-khan-7-things-to-know-about-humsafars-pretty-khirad-hussain-172850/ |date=20150924044508 }}. India.com.</ref>她在成為演員前是影片騎師及模特兒。瑪希拉在2011年首次演出電視喜劇《Neeyat》並在次年擔任電視連續劇《Humsafar》所女主角Khirad Hussain。<ref>[http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/play/big-hit-2/ "In conversation with ‘Humsafar’ couple – Fawad Khan, Mahira Khan"] {{Wayback|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/play/big-hit-2/ |date=20141013012517 }}. The Indian Express. 10 October 2014.</ref>《Humsafar》大受歡迎亦使巴基斯坦電視連續劇開始在[[印度|印度]]流行。她在2014年和[[寶萊塢|寶萊塢]]巨星[[沙·魯克·罕|沙·魯克·罕]]合作拍摄了电影《[[枭雄_(电影)|枭雄]]》。<ref>[http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Pakistans-Mahira-Khan-with-Shah-Rukh-Khan-in-Raees/articleshow/45523729.cms "Pakistan’s Mahira Khan with Shah Rukh Khan in Raees"] {{Wayback|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/Pakistans-Mahira-Khan-with-Shah-Rukh-Khan-in-Raees/articleshow/45523729.cms |date=20210309153035 }}. The Times of India. 16 December 2014.</ref>她和前夫育有一子Azlaan。

